    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Three rounds of random sign-flip + Fast Walsh-Hadamard Transform. Produces a pseudo-random rotation in O(d log d) time. d_out is the smallest power of 2 &gt;= d_in (zero-padded as needed). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
